msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh... Would you be interested in my\n"
"class on interacting with voe in the world\n"
"outside this town?<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>OK, everyone!<2.pa>\n"
"Let's show our cute observer what we've\n"
"been learning in class!\n"
"Now then...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"You're walking down the street on your\n"
"way somewhere, and a handsome voe\n"
"you've never met approaches..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would wave casually to him but also\n"
"keep myself prepared in case he's a\n"
"distraction for a bandit ambush!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Excellent thinking, Pasha! That's a\n"
"prudent approach to a new situation.\n"
"\n"
"Remember that sometimes voe may look\n"
"suspicious but are just being wary due to\n"
"the sight of a daunting Gerudo."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would enthusiastically greet him,\n"
"approaching with a smile and with my\n"
"hands clearly empty!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Wow, Dina, that's a very optimistic\n"
"approach to take!\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>Being overtly friendly is an excellent way\n"
"to put the stranger's mind at ease."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would walk casually toward him and\n"
"then strike a fierce blow when he least\n"
"suspected it!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Risa...<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"That would be a crime..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh... Are you interested in sitting in on\n"
"my class \"Voe and You\"? It may even\n"
"teach you a thing or two!\n"
"There's no hurryâ€”we won't be starting\n"
"until everyone has arrived."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Do you already care deeply for\n"
"someone?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>These young vai have never even met a\n"
"voe before.\n"
"\n"
"It's my duty to help prepare them for\n"
"what they'll encounter in the world\n"
"beyond Gerudo Town, good and bad."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk11"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, are you interested in the classes I\n"
"teach to vai before they set off from\n"
"Gerudo Town?\n"
"I teach a cooking class at my house at\n"
"night. If you want, please stop by!"
msgstr ""

