msgid ""
"<1.so>They say that a Gerudo who masters\n"
"making <2.se_co>creamy heart soup<3.re_co> can master\n"
"almost anything in the world.\n"
"I know you need some <4.se_co>fresh milk<5.re_co>, one\n"
"<6.se_co>voltfruit<7.re_co>, one "
"<8.se_co>hydromelon<9.re_co>...<10.pa>and\n"
"two <11.se_co>heart-shaped vegetables<12.re_co>...<13.pa>\n"
"<14.so>But I just can't seem to remember...<15.pa>\n"
"Grrr, what was that heart-shaped\n"
"vegetable?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
