msgid ""
"<1.so>Hmm...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I was planning on <2.se_co>creamy heart soup <3.re_co>for\n"
"the lesson today, but I'm being a bit\n"
"forgetful, it seems.\n"
"I know that I need some <4.se_co>fresh milk<5.re_co>, one\n"
"<6.se_co>voltfruit<7.re_co>, one <8.se_co>hydromelon<9.re_co>, and two\n"
"heart-shaped vegetables...\n"
"I just can't recall what the heart-shaped \n"
"vegetable was...<10.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<11.so>Well, I'm sure it'll come back to me\n"
