msgctxt "talk23"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, it's you. Did you want to observe\n"
"the \"Voe and You\" class?<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk24"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Attention, everyone! <2.pa>Let's get started!\n"
"We can show this cute vai what we've\n"
"been learning in class!\n"
"Now then...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"In your travels, you come upon an\n"
"injured voe lying on the ground. What do\n"
"you do?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk25"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I immediately lift him up over my\n"
"shoulder and carry him to the nearest\n"
"person who can treat him!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk26"
msgid ""
"<1.so>That's a very proactive answer, Pasha!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Always be aware that an injured person\n"
"may have non-visible injuries before you\n"
"move them, though!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk27"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would determine what was the matter\n"
"and make a medicine on the spot\n"
"to treat him!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk28"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Great answer, Dina!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Just be careful that the voe doesn't have\n"
"some sort of allergy to the ingredients\n"
"in your medicine!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk29"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would secretly bring him back to my\n"
"home, where I could help him gradually\n"
"recover! "
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk30"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Risa...<2.pa>\n"
"A sweet sentiment...<3.pa>\n"
"But also basically kidnapping."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "talk31"
msgid ""
"<1.so>During the day, it's \"Voe and You.\"\n"
"At night it's the cooking classes.\n"
"\n"
"People around me say it's a bit much,\n"
"but I say as long as there is something to\n"
"learn, why not keep learning?<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk32"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Attention, everyone! <2.pa>Let's get started!\n"
"We can show this cute vai what we've\n"
"been learning in class!\n"
"Now then...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"You are suddenly approached by a voe\n"
"whose attention you've sought, and he\n"
"abruptly engages you in conversation."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk33"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hrm...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would pretend that I don't know how to\n"
"speak his language."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk34"
msgid ""
"<1.so>That's an interesting approach, Pasha!<2.pa>\n"
"You could inspire some curiosity in the\n"
"voe by doing that...\n"
"Remember: it isn't unrealistic that the\n"
"voe may actually speak the language you\n"
"pretend to know, too!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk35"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would take the up-close opportunity to\n"
"determine his social standing based on\n"
"the clothes he's wearing!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk36"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ah, good thinking, Dina.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Just remember that sometimes all of\n"
"someone's good clothes are dirty, so\n"
"they might wear something more casual."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk37"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would grab his hand and twist his wrist\n"
"until he agreed to marry me!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk38"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Wha...<2.pa> You'd...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Risa... Let's talk after class."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "talk39"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh... Are you interested in taking my\n"
"class \"Voe and You\"?<2.pa>\n"
"I'm Ashai.\n"
"During the day I teach a class on the\n"
"voe of the world, and at night I teach\n"
"cooking classes.\n"
"<3.so>Why don't you join us?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk40"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Heehee...<2.pa>\n"
"You're wearing such an innocent\n"
"expression, but you understand, yeah?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "talk41"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, dear...<2.pa>\n"
"It sounds like you don't yet understand.\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>Perhaps you should consider taking my\n"
"lessons, hm?"
msgstr ""

